item.title: Inactivated vaccines for tilapia
item.description: My research project for my master thesis at AIT consists of developping whole cell killed vaccines against the bacterium Aeromonas veronii and the bacterium Streptoccocus agalactiae and study the immune response of the tilapia to the vaccines for monovalent and bivalent formulations.
